I'm still agreeing with you all here on this; Warriors need and should be kept a bit farther ahead stat-wise in our roles in groups and raids because that is &quot;why&quot; we are Warriors. If we could buff a group we would. If we could teleport people we would. If we could cast spells like every other hybrid ( ranger, pally, sk ) I am sure every spell we could possibly load would be casted in happiness.<br>
<br>
