The thread was already 5 pages long before it showed up on the FoH board.<br>
<br>
I have a feeling that someone just blew the lid off of an issue that warriors have been keeping to themselves for the most part, and has taken on a life of it's own, spreading to the FoH board, as someone saw that Furor contributed to the thread.  Since then, it's spilled over into Monkly Business, and probably other areas as well.<br>
